  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A controlled, double blinded study to determine the safety and reactogenicity in healthy
      adults of a single dose of a trivalent cell-derived influenza vaccine administered by
      intramuscular injection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
